    "title": "[Bug] Fix FlashInfer MNNVL socket collisions under concurrent vLLM jobs",
    "user": {
      "login": "yewentao256",
      "id": 44945378,
      "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQ0OTQ1Mzc4",
